## Remove submodule
# Run 
git rm <path-to-submodule>
# and commit.

## Add submodule
# any_name is there in case you need to rename the submodule
# folder_name is there in case you need to have submodule in different folder name instead of it's original name.
git submodule add --name any_name https://host.gitlab.com/any_repo.git folder_name
